Usage: report_voltage_swing [-help] -high_threshold <float>
                            -low_threshold <float> [-output_file <string>]
                            [-required_width {all clock}] [-view <string>]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-high_threshold <float>         # high threshold for voltage swing
                                # (float, required)
-low_threshold <float>          # low threshold for voltage swing
                                # (float, required)
-output_file <string>           # output file name (string, optional)
-required_width {all clock}     # type of report for voltage swing, default=all
                                # (enum, optional)
-view <string>                  # list of view names (string, optional)